---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
const title = "Pricing \u2014 Transparent fixed fees | Lodgedwell";
const description = "Fixed-fee conveyancing for Victoria. One clear professional fee per matter, with disbursements listed at cost. No hidden surprises.";
---
<Base title={title} description={description} active="pricing" tally={false}>
<main>
<section class="page-hero center">
  <span class="blob blob-1"></span>
  <span class="blob blob-2"></span>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head center reveal">
      <span class="eyebrow">Pricing</span>
      <h1>Fixed fees. No fine-print surprises.</h1>
      <p class="lead">One transparent professional fee per matter, quoted up front. Government and search fees (disbursements) are passed on at cost and listed separately — so you always know what you're paying for.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- PRICE TIERS -->
<section class="section" style="padding-top:16px">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="price-grid">
      <div class="price-card reveal">
        <span class="price-name">Sale</span>
        <p class="price-desc">Selling a Victorian home or investment property.</p>
        <div class="price-amount"><span class="cur">$</span><span class="num">880</span><span class="per">fixed*</span></div>
        <p class="price-note">+ disbursements at cost</p>
        <ul class="check-list">
          <li><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg>Section 32 vendor statement</li>
          <li><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg>Contract of sale prepared</li>
          <li><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg>Mortgage discharge coordinated</li>
          <li><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg>PEXA settlement managed</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/get-started#sell" class="btn btn--ghost btn--block">Start selling</a>
      </div>
      <div class="price-card featured reveal" data-delay="1">
        <span class="price-badge">Most popular</span>
        <span class="price-name">Purchase</span>
        <p class="price-desc">Buying your next home or investment in VIC.</p>
        <div class="price-amount"><span class="cur">$</span><span class="num">990</span><span class="per">fixed*</span></div>
        <p class="price-note">+ disbursements at cost</p>
        <ul class="check-list">
          <li><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg>Contract &amp; Section 32 review</li>
          <li><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg>Stamp duty &amp; concession checks</li>
          <li><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg>Lender liaison &amp; adjustments</li>
          <li><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg>PEXA settlement &amp; title transfer</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/get-started#buy" class="btn btn--block">Start buying</a>
      </div>
      <div class="price-card reveal" data-delay="2">
        <span class="price-name">Transfer</span>
        <p class="price-desc">Adding, removing or gifting a name on title.</p>
        <div class="price-amount"><span class="cur">$</span><span class="num">660</span><span class="per">fixed*</span></div>
        <p class="price-note">+ disbursements at cost</p>
        <ul class="check-list">
          <li><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg>Related-party &amp; family transfers</li>
          <li><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg>Duty &amp; exemption checks</li>
          <li><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg>Transfer documents prepared</li>
          <li><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg>Title lodgement handled</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/get-started" class="btn btn--ghost btn--block">Enquire now</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="center" style="margin-top:26px;font-size:.86rem;color:var(--muted);max-width:640px;margin-inline:auto">*Indicative fixed professional fees shown for illustration only. You'll receive a firm, itemised quote — including all disbursements — before any work begins. Replace with your final pricing.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- WHAT'S A DISBURSEMENT -->
<section class="section" style="background:var(--cream-200);border-block:1px solid var(--line)">
  <div class="container split">
    <div class="split-copy reveal">
      <span class="eyebrow">Total transparency</span>
      <h2>Fixed fee vs. disbursements</h2>
      <p class="lead">Two parts make up the cost of any conveyancing matter. We're upfront about both, so there are no surprises at settlement.</p>
      <div style="margin-top:26px">
        <div class="info-row"><span class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2v20M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6"/></svg></span><div><h4>Our fixed professional fee</h4><p>What you pay Lodgedwell for handling your matter end-to-end. Quoted up front and it doesn't change.</p></div></div>
        <div class="info-row"><span class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"/><path d="M14 2v6h6M9 13h6M9 17h4"/></svg></span><div><h4>Disbursements (at cost)</h4><p>Third-party fees we pay for you — title searches, certificates, PEXA and government lodgement fees. Listed line by line at exactly what they cost.</p></div></div>
        <div class="info-row"><span class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M3 3v18h18"/><path d="M7 14l3-3 3 3 5-5"/></svg></span><div><h4>Stamp duty (buyers)</h4><p>Paid to the State Revenue Office, not to us. We calculate it precisely and check every concession you're eligible for.</p></div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="split-media reveal" data-delay="1">
      <div class="card" style="padding:30px">
        <h3 style="margin-bottom:6px">Sample purchase quote</h3>
        <p style="font-size:.9rem;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:18px">Illustrative only</p>
        <div style="display:grid;gap:2px">
          <div class="mock-row" style="padding:14px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line)"><span>Fixed professional fee</span><b>$990</b></div>
          <div class="mock-row" style="padding:14px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line)"><span>Title searches &amp; certificates</span><b style="color:var(--muted);font-weight:600">~ $180</b></div>
          <div class="mock-row" style="padding:14px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line)"><span>PEXA &amp; lodgement fees</span><b style="color:var(--muted);font-weight:600">~ $150</b></div>
          <div class="mock-row" style="padding:14px 0;border-bottom:2px solid var(--line-strong)"><span>Land transfer (stamp) duty</span><b style="color:var(--muted);font-weight:600">SRO estimate</b></div>
          <div class="mock-row" style="padding:16px 0 0"><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--green-900)">You always see this before starting</span></div>
        </div>
        <a href="/get-started" class="btn btn--block" style="margin-top:22px">Get my exact quote</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- PRICING FAQ -->
<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head center reveal" style="margin-bottom:44px">
      <span class="eyebrow">Pricing questions</span>
      <h2>The fine print, in plain English</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="faq">
      <div class="faq-item reveal">
        <button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false">Is the fixed fee really fixed?<span class="plus"></span></button>
        <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Yes. Our professional fee is agreed in writing before we start and won't change for a standard matter. If something genuinely unusual comes up, we'll talk to you and agree any change before doing the work — never after.</p></div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item reveal">
        <button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false">What are disbursements?<span class="plus"></span></button>
        <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Disbursements are third-party costs we pay on your behalf — things like title searches, council and water certificates, and PEXA and government lodgement fees. We pass them on at cost and itemise every one, so you can see exactly where your money goes.</p></div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item reveal">
        <button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false">When do I pay?<span class="plus"></span></button>
        <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Typically our fees and disbursements are settled at the same time as your property settlement, so there's nothing to pay just to get started. We'll confirm the exact arrangement in your engagement.</p></div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item reveal">
        <button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false">Do you charge for an initial quote?<span class="plus"></span></button>
        <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Never. Completing the online form and receiving a firm, itemised quote is completely free and with no obligation. You only proceed if you're happy.</p></div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CTA -->
<section class="cta-band section-sm">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="cta-inner reveal">
      <h2>Get your exact, itemised quote</h2>
      <p>It's free and takes minutes. Start online and a licensed conveyancer will confirm your fixed fee within one business day.</p>
      <div class="cta-actions">
        <a href="/get-started#buy" class="btn btn--coral btn--lg">Quote for buying</a>
        <a href="/get-started#sell" class="btn btn--ghost btn--lg">Quote for selling</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
</main>
</Base>
